OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMostly cloudy with outbreaks of
OL,6,Frain, heaviest and most persistent
OL,7,Facross western parts, the rain turning
OL,8,Fmore showery in the afternoon, with a
OL,9,Frisk of thunder. Occasionally fresh
OL,10,Fsoutherly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FIt will remain cloudy during
OL,13,Fthe evening and through the night with
OL,14,Foutbreaks of heavy and perhaps
OL,15,Fthundery rain. Clearer, drier spells
OL,16,Fin the west towards morning.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
