OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FCloud and heavy, showery
OL,6,Fovernight rain clearing north in the
OL,7,Fmorning. Then sunny spells and
OL,8,Fscattered showers, these heavy at
OL,9,Ftimes.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FDry
OL,12,Fand bright start Monday before cloud
OL,13,Fand outbreaks of rain through the day.
OL,14,FVariable cloud, sunny spells and
OL,15,Foccasionally heavy showers Tuesday.
OL,16,FFurther rain or showers on Wednesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
